CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1953, pg. 14 reads: "Home Service Fair Prize-Winners, Demonstrator - Prize-winners at the four sessions of the Courier's 1953 Home Service Fair were so numerous that it would be impossible for the Courier to print pictures of all of them. However, here are pictures of just a few who won prizes. In the left photo are three winners of baskets shown with Gordon Phillips of the courier staff.  The winners are Mrs. Rebecca Moss, Miss Lois Peteusad and Mrs. Madeleine B. Walker...All Photos by Harris"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Gordon Phillips, presenting baskets to Rebecca Moss, Lois Peteusad, and Madeleine B. Walker, posed in front of stage with Jessie Vann on left, during the 1953 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair, Ammon Center
